---
title: Sichuan Beef Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: Is it time to lift your stir-fry game? Here's a delicious lesson in how to get crispy beef strips, tender veggies and a flavour-packed sauce. With a few simple tricks – cooking the meat in batches, getting the veggies started before adding the sauce and adding flavour to the rice with garlic – you'll be a stir-fry superstar in no time!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/suchuan-beef-stir-fry-0c5ac28a.jpg
